          For 2025/26, the most-used UK tax calculators cover take-home pay (income tax + NI +
          student loans), pension pot projections, and stamp duty. Boring Math offers all of these
          free with no account required. For salary earners, start with the UK Tax Calculator. For
          earners above &pound;100k, the 100k Tax Trap Calculator shows the 60% effective rate
          clearly. All calculators are updated for the 2025/26 tax year.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="ranked-list">
        <h2>Top 7 UK Tax Calculators for 2025/26</h2>
